tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE machine_learning_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    feature_1 FLOAT,
    feature_2 FLOAT,
    feature_3 FLOAT,
    label INT
)

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID,
    dataset_id UUID,
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES model (id),
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES dataset (id)
);

CREATE TABLE training_history (
    training_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    training_duration INTERVAL,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE hyperparameters (
    hyper_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    learning_rate FLOAT,
    batch_size INT,
    optimizer VARCHAR(50),
    epochs INT
);

CREATE TABLE evaluation_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    evaluation_date DATE,
    precision FLOAT,
    recall FLOAT,
    f1_score FLOAT
);
